  Subagent Configuration
  Choose how proactively Codex delegates codebase exploration.

  1. Prefer          Default to explorer subagents for read-only repository
                     discovery.
› 2. Auto (current)  Use explorer subagents for large or multi-topic
                     repository discovery.
  3. Less            Use explorer subagents only when explicitly requested.
  4. Disable         Do not proactively use explorer subagents for codebase
                     discovery.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
